application.model

Class Zone

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.model.Zone

  • public class Zone
extends java.lang.Object
    The Zone class is a representation of a zone that is used by the Park class. Each zone has a name, a code, and a threat level. The zone class contains an Override of the toString() method and has the following accessors and mutators: getZoneName, setZoneName, getZoneCode, setZoneCode, getThreatLevel, setThreatLevel.
    Author:
    Ivy Vasquez Sandoval (egi444) UTSA CS 3443 - Lab 8 Spring 2019
